title: Cybster.TV.Season.1.Complete.720p.-CYBSTER
description:
Welcome to the Cybster TV Season 1 Archive.

Please enjoy the shows from the late 2000's by Cybster DJ.

The original website at www.cybster.tv is no longer valid. I will be working on bringing a new website online at www.tv.cybster.com in the future... it may even be ready when you read this file.

This show was released on a monthly basis in 2008 and 2009 and was seen by thousands of music fans around the world. All the artist were independent and gave permission to be included on the show.

There is a possiblility of a Season 2 in the future so stay tuned. - Cybster DJ

All the files in this Archive a optismised and Tagged for iTunes... just drop them in.

Please follow Cybster DJ at these Social Networks...


I would appreciate if you can seed as much as possible
